text: Sieme Zijm (born 25 January 1978 in Den Helder, North Holland) is a former Dutch footballer who last played for FC Emmen. His former clubs are Go Ahead Eagles, FC Zwolle, Sparta Rotterdam, Excelsior Rotterdam and FC Dordrecht. ==See also== * Sparta Rotterdam season 2001–02 ==References== *Profile Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch footballers Category:AZ Alkmaar players Category:PEC Zwolle players Category:SBV Excelsior players Category:Sparta Rotterdam players Category:Go Ahead Eagles players Category:FC Emmen players Category:FC Dordrecht players Category:Eredivisie players Category:Eerste Divisie players Category:People from Den Helder Category:Association football defenders Category:Association football midfielders
